metadata.name: #01 - TurboPurple
metadata.description:
The TurboPurple is a Japanese car with 8 cylinders and 615 horsepower. 

It has 3rd place in international car racing in 2019.
It has not been participating in the races for the last 2 years, but his goal in the race in 2022 is to get the first trophy.
